{{catmain|Regulation of sport}}
Rules and/or regulations that are publicly agreed upon sets of principles, policies, criteria, descriptions and/or conducts governing a [[sport]] or physical activity for reasons of [[safety]], [[sportsmanship]], [[Sports equipment|equipment]] or [[Playing field|facility design]], and competitiveness.

