{{notability|date=February 2016}}
'''Athletomics''' is a field of [[omics]] dedicated to the examination of [[genomics]] and [[epigenomics]] variants associated to elite [[athletic]] performance and [[injury]] predisposition.

The first initiative to launch a large collaborative athletomics effort was the establishment of the [http://www.athlomeconsortium.org/ Athlome Project Consortium].

