{{catdiffuse}} Musical genres may be categorised according to *Place *Time *Outstanding characteristics such as "for dancing", "for accordions" etc. *Extra-musical function and context, such as "political music", "wedding music" etc. *Membership of larger genre: "be-bop" is a member of "jazz".
